snippet.title: Best VGM 2243 - Viewtiful Joe 2 - Ice Edge (The Polar Movie Land Theme)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

GameCube / PS2
Viewtiful Joe 2 (2004)
Ice Edge (The Polar Movie Land Theme)
Sayaka Morita & Masami Ueda

Twitter: https://twitter.com/SupraDarky
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SupraDarky
Bandcamp: https://supradarky.bandcamp.com/
